      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tIn the course of the history of the United States four Presidents have been assassinated, within less than 100 years, beginning with Abraham Lincoln in 1865. Attempts were also made on the lives of two other Presidents, one President-elect, and one ex-President.<br/>\n至今46總統，4位被刺殺，兩位有遇刺，一位還沒宣示的有遇刺，還有一位前總統遇刺，這就加起來有8個了，8/46=0.17，大概五位總統中就有一位遇刺這概率比蠟大佐屠支還高了，所以人美帝是武德高地真不是說說而已\t\t</div>",
